<tr><td></td><td>TEASER</td></tr>
<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Planet surface</td></tr>
<tr id="L1"><td><a href="#L1">1</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: Kirk, McCoy, Chekov and a security guard have beamed down to a planet with a green sky and occasional outcrops of vertical rocks. Their phasers are drawn.</td></tr>

<tr id="L2"><td><a href="#L2">2</a></td><td>KIRK:  Report, Mister Chekov.</td></tr>

<tr id="L3"><td><a href="#L3">3</a></td><td>CHEKOV:  Full scan. Results negative. Radiation level normal. Atmosphere and terrain are undisturbed. No evidence of a colony nor any residual aftereffect of a force that might have annihilated it.</td></tr>

<tr id="L4"><td><a href="#L4">4</a></td><td>KIRK:  Life readings, Doctor McCoy?</td></tr>

<tr id="L5"><td><a href="#L5">5</a></td><td>MCCOY:  Nothing. They said they were being attacked by an unidentified ship.</td></tr>

<tr id="L6"><td><a href="#L6">6</a></td><td>CHEKOV:  Which we were unable to detect upon approach.</td></tr>

<tr id="L7"><td><a href="#L7">7</a></td><td>KIRK:  An entire human colony, a whole settlement. One hundred men, women and children. Who did it? And why? (communicator beep) Kirk here.</td></tr>

<tr id="L8"><td><a href="#L8">8</a></td><td>SPOCK [OC]:  Spock here, Captain.</td></tr>

<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Bridge</td></tr>
