<tr id="L18"><td><a href="#L18">18</a></td><td>KANG:  You attacked my ship! Four hundred of my crew dead. Kirk, my ship is disabled. I claim yours. You are now prisoners of the Klingon Empire against which you have committed a wanton act of war!</td></tr>

