<tr id="L31"><td><a href="#L31">31</a></td><td>CHEKOV:  Cossacks! Filthy Klingon murderers! You killed my brother Piotre. The Archanis Four research outpost. A hundred peaceful people massacred! Just like you did here. My brother, you killed my brother.</td></tr>

<tr id="L32"><td><a href="#L32">32</a></td><td>KANG:  And you volunteer to join him. That is loyalty.</td></tr>

