<tr id="L328"><td><a href="#L328">328</a></td><td>SOMEONE: Captain's log, stardate Armageddon. We must find a way to defeat the alien force of hate that has taken over the Enterprise. Stop the war now, or spend eternity in futile bloody violence.</td></tr>

