<tr id="L353"><td><a href="#L353">353</a></td><td>KIRK:  We can't get through the Klingon defences in time, unless. Spock. Intra-ship beaming from one section to another. It's possible?</td></tr>

<tr id="L354"><td><a href="#L354">354</a></td><td>SPOCK:  It has rarely been done because of the danger involved. Pinpoint accuracy is required. If the transportee should materialise inside a solid object, a deck or wall.</td></tr>

