<tr id="L386"><td><a href="#L386">386</a></td><td>KIRK:  All right. All right. In the heart. In the head. I won't stay dead. Next time I'll do the same to you. I'll kill you. And it goes on, the good old game of war, pawn against pawn! Stopping the bad guys. While somewhere, something sits back and laughs and starts it all over again.</td></tr>

<tr id="L387"><td><a href="#L387">387</a></td><td>MCCOY:  Let's jump him.</td></tr>

<tr id="L388"><td><a href="#L388">388</a></td><td>SPOCK:  Those who hate and fight must stop themselves, Doctor. Otherwise, it is not stopped.</td></tr>

<tr id="L389"><td><a href="#L389">389</a></td><td>MARA:  Kang, I am your wife. I'm a Klingon. Would I lie for them? Listen to Kirk. He is telling the truth.</td></tr>

